column5: Well it started on opening day of bass season 2013 I said this bass season I am going to mostly fish for smallies as its been a few years since I got a real tank smallie !!! While I had no problems catching lots of them it's taken all season till yesterday and 13 different lakes I have fished to finally get her !!!! Anyways I got her and here she is and a very respectable 21inches !!!! And I got her up in north Haliburton caught photo& released !!! Tight-lines
Well done Shawn, she's a beaut !!
